# Hype-Stream Infinite Scroll Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Implement a TikTok-style "vertical deck" infinite scroll shopping experience. This feature, "Scroll to Shop," will serve as a high-engagement interface blending product discovery (Type A), brand vibe (Type B), and visual art (Type C). It focuses on gesture-based interactions (swipe to cart, double-tap to heart) and gamification to increase user dwell time.

## User Review Required
- **Dependencies**: I plan to use `framer-motion` (already in package.json) for all animations. If complex gestures (like hold-to-pause vs tap) become tricky, I might need to add `react-use-gesture`, but I'll start without it.
- **Assets**: I will use placeholder images/videos unless specific assets are provided. The plan assumes "mock" content for now.

